{
  "topic_id": "6_end",
  "title": "第六章基础交互逻辑",
  "description_md": "综合练习：实现一个可以记录用户输入与点击行为的交互页面。\n\n要求：\n- 用户可以输入猫咪名字；\n- 点击按钮后，页面展示输入的名字；\n- 点击次数也会在页面中显示并递增；\n\n通过本题，你将使用按钮监听、输入获取与 DOM 内容更新等 JS 操作。",
  "start_code": {
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>猫咪命名器</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>给你的猫咪取个名字吧</h1>\n  <input type=\"text\" id=\"cat-name-input\" placeholder=\"输入名字...\">\n  <button id=\"submit-btn\">提交名字</button>\n  <p id=\"result\"></p>\n  <p id=\"click-count\">点击次数：0</p>\n\n  <script>\n    let count = 0;\n    document.getElementById('submit-btn').addEventListener('click', function () {\n      const name = document.getElementById('cat-name-input').value;\n      document.getElementById('result').textContent = `你的猫咪名是：${name}`;\n      count++;\n      document.getElementById('click-count').textContent = `点击次数：${count}`;\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
    "css": "",
    "js": ""
  },
  "checkpoints": [
